  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA33">
<l>tuṇintatu cintai tuḻāyalaṅka laṅka</l>
<l>maṇintavaṉpē ruḷḷattup palkāṟ – paṇintatuvum</l>
<l>vēypiṟaṅku cāral viṟalvēṅ kaṭavaṉaiyē</l>
<l>vāytiṟaṅkaḷ collum vakai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Concentrated is [my] mind, inwardly, on the names of him who decorates</l>
<l>[his] body with tulsi garlands, and it humbled itself many times</l>
<l>before the one from victorious Vēṅkatam, with bamboo-glittering slopes,</l>
<l>in the [same] way that [my] mouth speaks of [his] qualities.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
